**CRITICAL: Modular Section Components**
- **Always create separate components** for each major page section
- **File naming convention**: `[section-name]-section.tsx` (e.g., `hero-section.tsx`, `welcome-section.tsx`)
- **Single responsibility**: Each component handles one specific section/feature
- **Import pattern**: Import and compose sections in page files, never write sections directly in pages
- **Reusability**: Design sections to be potentially reusable across different pages
- **Maintainability**: Keep section components under 200 lines when possible

